{"title":"czq的骡马区间","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020小学期","数据结构","STL","前缀和"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1229#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1229","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1229/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1229/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1229"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"czq获得了一个数列$a_i$，他定义骡马区间（~~既不神圣也不罗马更非区间~~）$[l,r]$为满足以下条件的区间：\r\n\r\n1.$a_l=a_r,l < r$\r\n\r\n2.$\\forall i$满足$l < i < r$，有$a_i \\neq a_l$\r\n\r\n我们定义一个区间$[l,r]$的奥斯曼和为$\\sum\\limits_{i=l}^r a_i$，czq想让你求出所有骡马区间的奥斯曼和的和。\r\n\r\n"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个整数$n$，为数列的长度。\r\n\r\n接下来一行$n$个整数，为数列的数$a_i$。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出仅一个整数，为答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"### 样例输入\r\n```\r\n4\r\n1 2 1 2\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 样例输出\r\n```\r\n9\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\leq n \\leq 10^5$\r\n\r\n$1 \\leq a_i \\leq 10^8$"}]}